		<id>http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Jawed_terror/doc&amp;diff=40470</id>
		<title>Jawed terror/doc</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Jawed_terror/doc&amp;diff=40470"/>
		<updated>2022-06-25T15:13:53Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Mrstickman1997: Removed useless note and added proper info and tips.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div&gt;* One of the few aggressive water creatures, jawed terrors are extremely dangerous for any survivors swimming in their territories; [[river]]s and [[lake]]s, luckily they are rare, but you don't want to be caught swimming wherever these monsters may be, this is why boats are encouraged more after the cataclysm, they cannot leave their water habitats, this can be used to the players advantage when killing them.&lt;/div&gt;</summary>
