		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Mrstickman1997: Added a couple tips.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div&gt;{{Tool&lt;br /&gt;
 |name=pocket knife&lt;br /&gt;
 |id=pockknife&lt;br /&gt;
 |glyph=&amp;lt;nowiki&amp;gt;;&amp;lt;/nowiki&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
 |color=c_blue&lt;br /&gt;
 |volume=0&lt;br /&gt;
