&lt;br /&gt;
{{quote|A small pocket knife, not great for combat, but better than nothing.}}&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
It can be used for butchering, and also to cauterize wounds (along with a [[lighter]]). Due to it's low damage, it is more useful as a tool than a weapon, using this as a weapon is suicide, one may want to bring a [[makeshift knife]] alongside a pocket knife as a cutting weapon as the pocket knife has better butchering quality, and has fine cutting 1, where the makeshift knife doesn't.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
