	<entry>
		<id>http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Dazed&amp;diff=40388</id>
		<title>Dazed</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Dazed&amp;diff=40388"/>
		<updated>2022-05-12T16:34:12Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Mrstickman1997: It's the screecher zombie that does this, not a shrieker...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div&gt;'''Dazed''' is a [[effects|status effect]] applied by, most frequently, a sonic attack that puts you in a state of shock.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
{{igs|&amp;quot;You're visibly shaken up, and are having a hard time focusing on what's going on around you.&amp;quot;}}&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
* Applied by a sonic attack of a shrieking creature like a [[screecher zombie]].&lt;br /&gt;
** Also applied as a side effect of the [[Magiclysm|Magiclysm mod's]] spell [[Lesser Quantum Tunnel]].&lt;br /&gt;
* Maximum intensity is 10, increments by 2 past the first level.&lt;br /&gt;
* Effects:&lt;br /&gt;
** perception -5&lt;br /&gt;
** dexterity -3&lt;br /&gt;
** speed -3 per each level of intensity above first&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
{{Effects}}&lt;br /&gt;
[[Category:Effects]]&lt;/div&gt;</summary>
		<author><name>Mrstickman1997</name></author>
		
	</entry>
