	<entry>
		<id>http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Brazier&amp;diff=40353</id>
		<title>Brazier</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Brazier&amp;diff=40353"/>
		<updated>2022-04-28T15:34:00Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Mrstickman1997: Smoke doesn't spread far or last very long.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div&gt;{{Tool&lt;br /&gt;
 |name=brazier&lt;br /&gt;
 |id=brazier&lt;br /&gt;
 |glyph=&amp;lt;nowiki&amp;gt;;&amp;lt;/nowiki&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
 |color=c_ltred&lt;br /&gt;
 |volume=6&lt;br /&gt;
 |weight=5066&lt;br /&gt;
 |bash=11&lt;br /&gt;
 |cut=0&lt;br /&gt;
 |tohit=1&lt;br /&gt;
 |rarity=0&lt;br /&gt;
 |price=900&lt;br /&gt;
 |mat1=iron&lt;br /&gt;
 |mat2=MNULL&lt;br /&gt;
 |func=&lt;br /&gt;
 |startammo=0&lt;br /&gt;
 |maxammo=0&lt;br /&gt;
 |ammotype=&lt;br /&gt;
 |drainturns=0&lt;br /&gt;
}}&lt;br /&gt;
{{quote|This is a large metal stand with slots on the side. You can set it somewhere through the construction menu and then set fires in it with no risk of spreading.}}&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
A large stand, with a shallow bowl on top. Used for old-school fire sources.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
It will still give off [[smoke]], but will prevent the [[fire]] from spreading, smoke will only spread from a brazier when the fuel starts burning, and does not travel far, it will eventually stop emitting smoke with the fire still burning, so simply stand back from the fire after freshly adding fuel or lighting the fire. Make sure to {{key|a}}ctivate it to place it down for this effect, not {{key|d}}rop it down. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
How to use a brazier:&lt;br /&gt;
 1. Deploy it {{key|a}}. If you didn't, the game will warn you when you go to set the fuel on fire.&lt;br /&gt;
 2. Drop fuel in brazier&lt;br /&gt;
 3. Set fuel in brazier on fire&lt;br /&gt;
 4. Enjoy and don't burn to death.&lt;br /&gt;
Don't worry about the order too much, as long as step 2 and 3 come last. You can set the fuel down and then set the brazier.&lt;br /&gt;
Found on either sides of the altar of churches. Brimstone not included. Flammable benches included.&lt;br /&gt;
{{Craft&lt;br /&gt;
 |ComponentR=[[sheet metal]]&lt;br /&gt;
 |Tool=[[rock]] '''OR''' [[stone hammer]] '''OR''' [[hammer]] '''OR''' [[hatchet]] '''OR''' [[integrated toolset]]&lt;br /&gt;
 |Skill1=fabrication&lt;br /&gt;
 |SkillLvl1=1&lt;br /&gt;
}}&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
{{Tools}}&lt;br /&gt;
