	<entry>
		<id>http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Cabin&amp;diff=40285</id>
		<title>Cabin</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://cddawiki.chezzo.com/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Cabin&amp;diff=40285"/>
		<updated>2022-03-22T12:23:15Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Mrstickman1997: They don't protect well from summer and winter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;lt;noinclude&amp;gt;{{Map&amp;lt;/noinclude&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;lt;includeonly&amp;gt;{{row/Map1&amp;lt;/includeonly&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
 |name=cabin&lt;br /&gt;
 |glyph=&amp;lt;nowiki&amp;gt;C&amp;lt;/nowiki&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
 |color=i_green&lt;br /&gt;
 |seecost=5&lt;br /&gt;
 |extras=build_extras&lt;br /&gt;
}}&amp;lt;noinclude&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Forest cabin and a tool shed. {{spoiler|You'll have to kill the former (undead) inhabitants if you want to settle here.}} Somewhat questionable to take shelter in, since they do not have any guaranteed water source as the [[LMOE shelter]] does. However, if you have/make a [[funnel]] and water container, [[river]], [[lake]] or [[swamp]] nearby alongside (as appropriate) a means to purify the water, then you could survive, as the rest of the forest has the natural resources to keep you alive.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
If staying in a cabin, players should note that it unless it has a [[cabin basement|basement]], which is rare in most cabins and quite dangerous due to [[cult]] monsters, cabins do not provide much protection from dangerous [[season]]s such as [[summer]] and [[winter]]; cabins will get very hot in summer and very cold during winter, therefore they will need to wear their weather protective clothing at all times in the cabin and keep blankets on their bed for winter.&lt;br /&gt;
[[Category:Wilderness]]&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;lt;/noinclude&amp;gt;&lt;/div&gt;</summary>
		<author><name>Mrstickman1997</name></author>
		
	</entry>
