PORTALS? Reports of shimmering gateways opening around the US have been corroborated by our own reporting staff. One reporter witnessed a creature the size of an apartment building taking a direct hit from an Apache helicopter's weaponry and continuing to fight. Government officials could not be reached for comment, but a local pastor spoke to our reporter in the field. &amp;quot;There can no longer be any doubt,&amp;quot; she was quoted as saying. &amp;quot;These are the end times.&amp;quot; (241)&lt;br /&gt;
