}}&amp;lt;noinclude&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
== Notes ==&lt;br /&gt;
Light smoke protection: 92.58%&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Medium smoke protection: 61.72%&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Heavy smoke protection: 3.84%&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
While the smoke protection of this item is minuscule, and utterly useless against [[toxic gas]] and [[fungal haze]], wearing a dust mask decreases the chance of catching a [[low immunity diseases|cold or flu]], therefore one may want to wear this item whenever they can. &lt;br /&gt;
