&lt;br /&gt;
== Notes ==&lt;br /&gt;
*While this may have one of the highest storage capacities of any backpack, this bag is VERY encumbering, don't try fighting zombies too often while wearing this...&lt;br /&gt;
*Best used for non-combative [[scavenging]] trips, or when moving to a new base if you don't have a vehicle yet.&lt;br /&gt;
*Can be crafted quite early in the tailoring skill compared to other storage clothing.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
== Changes ==&lt;br /&gt;
* {{InlineVer|0.8}} - Added.&lt;br /&gt;
